name: Bara
description:
Forged in fire, 

Bara became one of the high skilled assassins under the Saka Kingdom led by Prabu Saar. However, Queen Tyas did not like Bara because of his attitude and arrogance. Because of his appearance in battle, Prabu Saar entrusted Bara. 

Until one day, during the war, Prabu Saar was dying of an illness which could be cured with a Holy Relic (Keris). Queen Tyas decided to send Bara and Tirta on an expedition to find Keris.
